0.1.name: wordpress/tdd-progress-bar
0.1.description: TDD Progress Bar allows you to track the progress of multiple projects. Actually, as many as you'd like. A cool feature is the ability to "race" multiple projects at once. Progress bars are managed in the admin side and displayed using shortcode. Oh, and did I mention it has a very pretty animation?
